 whose verses have been detailed, an Arabic Qur’ān for a people who know,\",\"translation_de\":\"ein Buch, dessen Zeichen ausführlich dargelegt sind, als ein arabischer Qur’an, für Leute, die Bescheid wissen,\",\"translation_tr\":\"(Bu,) bilen bir kavim için, âyetleri Arapça okunarak açıklanmış bir kitaptır.\",\"translation_fr\":\"un Livre aux versets détaillés, un Coran arabe pour des gens qui savent,\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":4,\"end\":9},{\"class\":\"idgham-bilaghunnah\",\"start\":42,\"end\":45},{\"class\":\"idgham-bilaghunnah\",\"start\":46,\"end\":48},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":54,\"end\":59},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":66,\"end\":68}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":2}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"3\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":4222,\"number\":4,\"text\":\"بَشِيْرًا وَّنَذِيْرًاۚ فَاَعْرَضَ اَكْثَرُهُمْ فَهُمْ لَا يَسْمَعُوْنَ\",\"translation_id\":\"yang membawa berita gembira dan peringatan. Akan tetapi, kebanyakan mereka berpaling (darinya) serta tidak mendengarkan.\",\"juz_id\":24,\"surah_id\":41,\"transliteration\":\"basyîraw wa nadzîrâ, fa a‘radla aktsaruhum fa hum lâ yasma‘ûn\",\"translation_en\":\"As a giver of good tidings and a warner; but most of them turn away, so they do not hear.\",\"translation_de\":\"als Frohboten und als Warner. Aber die meisten von ihnen wenden sich ab, so daß sie nicht hören.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Bu kitap müjdeleyici ve uyarıcıdır. Fakat onların çoğu yüz çevirdi, artık dinlemezler.\",\"translation_fr\":\"annonçant l’heureuse nouvelle (aux hommes) et les avertissant mais la plupart d’entre eux se détournent, car ils n’entendent pas.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":6,\"end\":8},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":9,\"end\":11},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":19,\"end\":21},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":23,\"end\":25},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":67,\"end\":69}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":3}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"4\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":4223,\"number\":5