uh Allah digiring ke neraka, lalu mereka dipisah-pisahkan.\",\"juz_id\":24,\"surah_id\":41,\"transliteration\":\"wa yauma yuḫsyaru a‘dâ'ullâhi ilan-nâri fa hum yûza‘ûn\",\"translation_en\":\"And [mention, O Muḥammad], the Day when the enemies of Allāh will be gathered to the Fire while they are [driven], assembled in rows,\",\"translation_de\":\"Und (denke an) den Tag, da Allahs Feinde zum (Höllen)feuer versammelt und in Reihen gebracht werden.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Allah'ın düşmanları, ateşe sürülmek üzere toplandıkları gün, hepsi bir araya getirilirler.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Le jour où les ennemis d’Allah seront rassemblés en foule devant le Feu, ils y seront précipités.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"madd-wajib\",\"start\":24,\"end\":26},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":45,\"end\":47},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":67,\"end\":69}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":18}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"19\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":4238,\"number\":20,\"text\":\"حَتّٰىٓ اِذَا مَا جَاۤءُوْهَا شَهِدَ عَلَيْهِمْ سَمْعُهُمْ وَاَبْصَارُهُمْ وَجُلُوْدُهُمْ بِمَا كَانُوْا يَعْمَلُوْنَ\",\"translation_id\":\"Ketika mereka sampai ke neraka, pendengaran, penglihatan, dan kulit mereka menjadi saksi terhadap apa yang telah mereka lakukan.\",\"juz_id\":24,\"surah_id\":41,\"transliteration\":\"ḫattâ idzâ mâ jâ'ûhâ syahida ‘alaihim sam‘uhum wa abshâruhum wa julûduhum bimâ kânû ya‘malûn\",\"translation_en\":\"Until, when they reach it, their hearing and their eyes and their skins will testify against them of what they used to do.\",\"translation_de\":\"Wenn sie dann dort angekommen sind, legen ihr Gehör, ihre Augen und ihre Häute gegen sie Zeugnis ab über das, was sie zu tun pflegten.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Nihayet oraya geldikleri zaman kulakları, gözleri ve derileri, işledikleri şeye karşı onların aleyhine şahitlik edecektir.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Une fois qu’ils y arriveront, leur ouïe, leurs yeux et leurs peaux témoigneront contre eux (dénonçant) ce qu’ils faisaient.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"clas